title: DOLL$BOXX - Dolls Apartment
description:
For any of you Babymetal fans looking to journey a little further I present 

DOLL$BOX..  Just simply amazing talents these girls are, every single instrument is played to perfection and wait till you hear the vocals... 

I included 1 video as I feel its the best intro to the band and the catchiest song- The rest of the album is great but this number really stands out
